name: BattleTech Classic 1980's look
description:
This model picks up the unique black-and-white line drawing style, which defined the look and feel of the early BattleTech technical readouts.

model is trained on a set of old fanart.

for example try prompts like "MechBattleTechClassicTR3025 in action on a battlefield with a city in the background"
